{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Lone Soul is a fast-paced action roguelike featuring a combo-based combat system and enhanced build variety through ARPG-style itemization. Each run takes you through a series of randomly generated locations, allowing you to craft a unique build with every playthrough.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237360/extras/gif_01_new_final.gif?t=1739219211\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Express Yourself in Combat</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">During your excursions into the mythical tower, you will acquire dozens of blessings to enhance your combo deck. Whether you favor close-quarters combat, tactical positioning, or commanding arcane forces, the choice is yours.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237360/extras/Gif_02.gif?t=1739219211\" /> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">It\u2019s Finally Time to Gear Up</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Every cleared room rewards you with precious loot that can be upgraded, traded, or even customized. The gear is fully randomized, ensuring each run feels fresh and unique while opening the door to limitless build possibilities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237360/extras/gif_04.gif?t=1739219211\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong></strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Three is Better Than One</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Each of the three floors of the mythical tower is guarded by a powerful keeper, but to reach its core, you must face thre